ZH: 我今天投稿了一篇文章给杂志编辑。
EN: I submitted an article to the magazine editor today.

ZH: 他的诗歌作品被投稿到一个文学网站上了。
EN: His poetry works were submitted to a literary website.

ZH: 这个论坛只接受会员投稿。
EN: This forum only accepts contributions from members.

ZH: 她投稿的小说很快就被出版社接受了。
EN: Her submitted novel was quickly accepted by a publishing house.

ZH: 他花了很多时间撰写并投稿这篇学术论文。
EN: He spent a lot of time writing and submitting this academic paper.

ZH: 我们鼓励读者积极参与，投稿自己的意见和想法。
EN: We encourage readers to actively participate and submit their own opinions and ideas.

ZH: 他的照片被选中并投稿到一本摄影集里。
EN: His photos were selected and submitted for a photography book.

ZH: 请在截止日期之前投稿你的作品。
EN: Please submit your work before the deadline.

ZH: 这个杂志现在正大量投稿关于旅游的文章。
EN: This magazine is now accepting a large number of travel-related article submissions.

ZH: 她花了很多时间在这个画册上投稿自己的作品。
EN: She spent a lot of time submitting her works for this art book.

ZH: 我们会对投稿进行审核，然后选择发布合适的内容。
EN: We will review the submissions and select appropriate content for publication.

ZH: 请仔细阅读投稿指南，了解有关格式和要求的信息。
EN: Please read the submission guidelines carefully to understand the formatting and requirements.

ZH: 这个网站为用户提供了一个平台，可以方便地投稿自己的创作。
EN: This website provides users with a platform to easily submit their own creations.

ZH: 他的摄影作品以投稿的形式被展示在一个艺术展览上。
EN: His photography works were showcased in an art exhibition in the form of submissions.

ZH: 很多读者都被邀请投稿到这个故事集中。
EN: Many readers were invited to contribute to this collection of stories.

