EN: He has always dreamed of one day being able to submit his work to internationally renowned magazines.

ZH: 作家们通过邮件将他们的投稿寄给编辑部。
EN: Writers send their submissions to the editorial office by mail.

ZH: 这个平台鼓励年轻人投稿，并提供激励机制。
EN: This platform encourages young people to submit their work and provides incentives.

ZH: 我们欢迎学生们为学校杂志投稿。
EN: We welcome students to submit contributions for the school magazine.
